{"article_id":"FzPsUmNp4EizHTuT","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"There were 15 of them .","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"Most arrived in the dead of night ,","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"laid their trap","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"and waited for the target to arrive .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"That target was Jamal Khashoggi , a prominent Saudi critic of his country ' s government and its young crown prince .","depth":3},{"id":5,"text":"Since his killing in Istanbul , Turkish media has released a steady drip feed of evidence","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"implicating Saudi officials .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"Weeks of investigation by The Times builds on that evidence","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"and reconstructs what unfolded , hour-by-hour .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"Our timeline shows the ruthless efficiency of a hit team of experts","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"that seemed specially chosen from Saudi government ministries .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Some had links to the crown prince himself .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"After a series of shifting explanations , Saudi Arabia now denies","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"that this brazen hit job was premeditated .","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"But this reconstruction of the killing , and the botched cover-up , calls their story into serious question .","depth":4},{"id":15,"text":"It ' s Friday morning , Sept. 28 .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Khashoggi and his fiancée , Hatice Cengiz , are at the local marriage office in Istanbul .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"In order to marry ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"he ' s told that he needs Saudi paperwork","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"and goes straight to the consulate","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"to arrange it .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"They tell him to return in a week .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"It all seems routine ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"but it ' s not .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"Inside there ' s a Saudi spy , Ahmed al-Muzaini ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"who ' s working under diplomatic cover .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"That very day , he flies off to Riyadh","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"and helps concoct a plan","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"to intercept Khashoggi","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"when he returns to the consulate .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Fast-forward to Monday night into Tuesday morning .","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"Saudi agents converge in Istanbul aboard separate flights .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"Muzaini , the spy , flies back from Riyadh .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"A commercial flight carries a three-man team","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"that we believe","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"flew from Cairo .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"Two of the men are security officers","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"and they ' ve previously traveled with the crown prince .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"A private jet","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"flying from Riyadh","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"lands around 3:30 a.m.","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"That plane is often used by the Saudi government ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"and it ' s carrying nine Saudi officials , some","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"who played key roles in Khashoggi ' s death .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"We ' ll get to Team 3 later on ,","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"and for now focus on these men from Team 2 .","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"This is Salah al-Tubaigy , a high-ranking forensics and autopsy expert in the Saudi interior ministry .","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"Turkish officials will later say","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"his role was to dismember Khashoggi ' s body .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"Another is Mustafa al-Madani , a 57-year-old engineer .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"As we ' ll see ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"it ' s no accident that he looks like Khashoggi .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"And this is Maher Mutreb , the leader of the operation .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"Our investigation into his past reveals a direct link between Mutreb and the Saudi crown prince .","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"When bin Salman toured a Houston neighborhood earlier this year ,","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"we discovered","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"that Mutreb was with him , a glowering figure in the background .","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"We found him again in Boston , at a U.N. meeting in New York , in Madrid and Paris , too .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"This global tour was all part of a charm offensive by the prince","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"to paint himself as a moderate reformer .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Back then , Mutreb was in the royal guard .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"Now , he would orchestrate Khashoggi ' s killing .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"And his close ties to the crown prince beg the question ,","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"just how high up the Saudi chain of command did the plot","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"to kill go ?","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Early Tuesday morning , Khashoggi flies back from a weekend trip to London .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"He and the Saudis nearly cross paths at the airport .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"The Saudi teams check into two hotels ,","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"which give quick access to the consulate .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"Khashoggi heads home with his fiancée .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"He ' d just bought an apartment for their new life together .","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"By mid-morning , the Saudis are on the move .","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"Mutreb leaves his hotel","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"three hours before Khashoggi is due at the consulate .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"The rest of the team isn ' t far behind .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"The building is only a few minutes away on foot ,","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"and soon , they ' re spotted at this entrance .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"Mutreb arrives first .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"Next , we see al-Tubaigy , the autopsy expert .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"And now al-Madani , the lookalike .","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"The stage is almost set .","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"A diplomatic car pulls out of the consulate driveway","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"and switches places with a van ,","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"which backs in .","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"Turkish officials say","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"this van would eventually carry away Khashoggi ' s remains .","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"From above , we can see","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"the driveway is covered ,","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"hiding any activity around the van from public view .","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"Meanwhile , Khashoggi and his fiancée set out for the consulate ,","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"walking hand-in-hand .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"In their final hour together , they chat about dinner plans and new furniture for their home .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"At 1:13 p.m. , they arrive at the consulate .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"Khashoggi gives her his cellphones","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"before he enters .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"He walks into the consulate .","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"It ' s the last time","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"we see him .","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"Inside , Khashoggi is brought to the consul general ' s office on the second floor .","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"The hit team is waiting in a nearby room .","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"Sources","depth":16},{"id":101,"text":"briefed on the evidence ,","depth":16},{"id":102,"text":"told us","depth":15},{"id":103,"text":"Khashoggi quickly comes under attack .","depth":14},{"id":104,"text":"He ' s dragged to another room","depth":15},{"id":105,"text":"and is killed within minutes .","depth":15},{"id":106,"text":"Then al-Tubaigy , the autopsy expert , dismembers his body","depth":15},{"id":107,"text":"while listening to music .","depth":15},{"id":108,"text":"Maher Mutreb makes a phone call to a superior .","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"He says ,","depth":15},{"id":110,"text":"\" Tell your boss , \"","depth":16},{"id":111,"text":"and \" The deed was done. \"","depth":16},{"id":112,"text":"Outside , the van","depth":17},{"id":113,"text":"reportedly carrying Khashoggi ' s body","depth":17},{"id":114,"text":"pulls out of the side entrance","depth":16},{"id":115,"text":"and drives away .","depth":15},{"id":116,"text":"At the same time , the Saudis begin trying to cover their tracks .","depth":14},{"id":117,"text":"While Khashoggi ' s fiancée waits here","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"where she left him ,","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"two figures leave from the opposite side .","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"One of them is wearing his clothes .","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"Later , the Saudis would claim","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"that this was Khashoggi .","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"But it ' s al-Madani , the engineer , now a body double","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"pretending","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"that the missing journalist left the consulate alive .","depth":14},{"id":126,"text":"Yet there ' s one glaring flaw :","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"The clothes are the same ,","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"but he ' s wearing his own sneakers , the ones","depth":15},{"id":129,"text":"he walked in with .","depth":15},{"id":130,"text":"Meanwhile , the van","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"that ' s allegedly carrying Khashoggi ' s body","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"makes the two-minute drive from the consulate to the Saudi consul ' s residence .","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"There ' s several minutes of deliberations","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"but the van eventually pulls into the building ' s driveway .","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"Again , it ' s hidden from public view .","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"It ' s now three hours since Khashoggi was last seen .","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"The body double hails this taxi","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"and continues weaving a false trail through the city .","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"He heads to a popular tourist area","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"and then changes back into his own clothes .","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"Later , we see him joking around in surveillance footage .","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"Over at the airport , more Saudi officials arrive on another flight from Riyadh .","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"They spend just five hours in Istanbul ,","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"but we ' re not sure where they go .","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"Now we pick up Maher Mutreb again ,","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"exiting from the consul ' s house .","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"It ' s time","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"for them to go .","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"Mutreb and others check out of their hotel","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"and move through airport security .","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"Al-Muzaini , the spy , heads to the airport too .","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"But","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"as they ' re leaving Istanbul ,","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"Khashoggi ' s fiancée is still outside the consulate ,","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"pacing in circles .","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"She ' ll soon raise the alarm","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"that Khashoggi is missing","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"and she ' ll wait for him until midnight .","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"The alarm spreads around the world .","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"Nine days later , the Saudis send another team to Istanbul .","depth":7},{"id":161,"text":"They say","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"it ' s to investigate what happened .","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"But among them are a toxicologist and a chemist ,","depth":8},{"id":164,"text":"who also has ties to the hit team .","depth":8},{"id":165,"text":"He and Tubaigy attended a forensics graduation days before Khashoggi was killed .","depth":7},{"id":166,"text":"Turkish officials later say","depth":6},{"id":167,"text":"that this team ' s mission was not to investigate ,","depth":7},{"id":168,"text":"but to cover up the killing .","depth":7},{"id":169,"text":"Now the Saudi story has changed ,","depth":6},{"id":170,"text":"and prosecutors are seeking the death penalty for several suspects in Khashoggi ' s killing .","depth":7},{"id":171,"text":"But that doesn ' t include Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman ,","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"who","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"many Western government officials are convinced","depth":10},{"id":174,"text":"authorized the killing .","depth":9},{"id":175,"text":"Khashoggi ' s remains still haven ' t been found .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":351,"left":190,"right":350,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":190,"left":180,"right":189,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":180,"left":179,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":0,"right":178,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":1,"right":177,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":177,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":189,"left":186,"right":188,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":186,"left":181,"right":185,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":182,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":184,"left":183,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":188,"left":187,"right":14,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":187,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":350,"left":239,"right":349,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":239,"left":218,"right":238,"relation":"joint","nuclear